HOPE YOU GOT THE LETTER AND ♪♪

26:12.973 --> 26:17.911
♪♪ I PRAY YOU CAN MAKE IT BETTER
DOWN HERE ♪♪

26:17.945 --> 26:23.217
♪♪ I DON'T MEAN A BIG REDUCTION
IN THE PRICE OF BEER ♪♪

26:23.250 --> 26:25.819
♪♪ BUT ALL THE PEOPLE
THAT YOU MADE IN YOUR IMAGE ♪♪

26:25.853 --> 26:28.589
♪♪ SEE THEM STARVING
ON THEIR FEET ♪♪

26:28.622 --> 26:35.429
